#   svm_model.joblib         ← Linear SVM  — 79.5% accuracy
#   naive_bayes_model.joblib ← Multinomial Naive Bayes — 72.6% accuracy
#   lstm_model.keras         ← LSTM neural net — 81.0% accuracy (default)
#
# Classes (5): Spam | Important | Work | Promotion | Personal
# Default model for POST /run: lstm
